parameters:
\SE[24]Oh, that was terrifying.... \SE[51]The sensation of my
body becoming cold and unable to move in the water.... \SE[37]For
the first time in my life, I was prepared for 'death'....

\SE[84]Hey... try something other than swimming in the waterway.
\.In this temperature, cold water swimming is for those who want
to commit suicide....

\SE[16]But, this is the fastest and most accurate! \SE[0]The
mission success rate is significantly higher than any other
route!

\SE[2]Why does Cat-san, who came through the same route, seem
completely fine...?

\SE\SE[15]I'm strong against the cold!! So, this level of cold is
nothing to me!!

\SE[4]By the way, where is Laura? \SE[75]She said she had some
free time... and it seems like she went over there.
\SE[2]I see.... \.Based on my prediction, maybe soon....

\SE[76]Geez... It's your own responsibility, right? \SE[51]If it
was just a retreat, Cat alone would have been enough.

\SE[64]I-I knew that... \!\SE[29]But I thought if I went at that
timing, it would be cool...

\SE[4]Your real performance is after this, right? \SE[75]...I
hope you can fight properly, okay?

\SE[16]Don't worry... I'm strong against the cold! \SE[13]I can
still work a lot more...!

\SE[4]Well...\.Laura and I are about to leave soon....
\!\SE[3]Who should we take with us?

\SE[4]Is there anyone who wants a break? \SE[7]We have two hands,
so don't hesitate to speak up.

\SE[80]Oh my, oh my... Looks like you're full of motivation.
\SE[3]I'm not sure who to take with us though...

\SE[4]Since we're at it... Let's have Laura decide. \SE[7]Come
on, appeal with your eyes.

\SE[4]If I make the decision, it might lack objectivity.
\!\SE[3]Being too close might dull my judgment. \.So, you see, \.
\SE[7]Choose two people.

\SE[24]Ugh... These stares are tough.... \SE[5]Alright, for the
first person....

\SE[2]The first person will be Ryan. Now, what about the second
person?

\SE[2]The first person will be Rebecca. Now, what about the
second person?

\SE[2]The first person will be Melissa. Now, what about the
second person?

\SE[2]The first person will be Lunaroa. Now, what about the
second person?

\SE[2]Understood. We'll go with this team. \SE[7]The remaining
two will support as backup with Cat.

\SE[11]You're suddenly making me choose... \!\SE[28]Haa... I'm so
nervous...
